elements.title: Idle Champions of the Forgotten Realms
elements.description: Idle Champions is a licensed Dungeons & Dragons strategy management video game uniting iconic characters from novels, campaigns, and shows into one epic adventure.

elements.title: Hundred Days - Winemaking Simulator
elements.description: Winemaking could be your best adventure. Make the best wine interacting with soil and nature and take your winery to the top. Your beautiful journey into the winemaking tradition starts now.

elements.title: Shadow of the Tomb Raider: Definitive Edition
elements.description: In Shadow of the Tomb Raider Definitive Edition experience the final chapter of Lara’s origin as she is forged into the Tomb Raider she is destined to be.

elements.title: Terraforming Mars
elements.description:
The taming of the Red Planet has begun!

Control your corporation, play project cards, build up production, place your cities and green areas on the map, and race for milestones and awards!

Will your corporation lead the way into humanity's new era?

elements.title: Car Mechanic Simulator 2018
elements.description: Build and expand your repair service empire in this incredibly detailed and highly realistic simulation game, where attention to car detail is astonishing. Find classic, unique cars in the new Barn Find module and Junkyard module.

elements.title: A Game Of Thrones: The Board Game Digital Edition
elements.description: It is the digital adaptation of the top-selling strategy board game from Fantasy Flight Games.

elements.title: ToeJam & Earl: Back in the Groove!
elements.description:
ToeJam & Earl: Back in the Groove is a mash-up of the best features from the classic console games with a ton of funky fresh improvements.

Relive the original roguelike game with new 4 player online and local co-op, crazy Earthlings, weird presents and aliens from Funkotron!

elements.title: Darkwood
elements.description: Darkwood - a new perspective on survival horror. Scavenge and explore a rich, ever-changing free-roam world by day, then hunker down in your hideout and pray for the morning light.

elements.title: Fallout 3: Game of the Year Edition
elements.description:
Prepare for the Future™
Experience the most acclaimed game of 2008 like never before with Fallout 3: Game of the Year Edition. Create a character of your choosing and descend into a post-apocalyptic world where every minute is a fight for survival

elements.title: Evoland Legendary Edition
elements.description: Evoland Legendary Edition brings you two great and unique RPGs, with their graphic style and gameplay changing as you progress through the game!
